    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": "Cough\n, with or without sputum, without evidence of\npneumonia\n, common cold, or\nasthma\nCough >5d is more suggestive of bronchitis than common cold\nCough may persist for 10-20d\nCough >3wk suggests\nasthma\n,\nCOPD\n,\npertussis\n, postnasal drip,\nGERD\nOften follows\nURI",
